00104 typedef volatile uint8_t register8_t;
00105 typedef volatile uint16_t register16_t;

00108 
00109 #ifdef _WORDREGISTER
00110 #undef _WORDREGISTER
00111 #endif
00112 #define _WORDREGISTER(regname)   \
00113     __extension__ union \
00114     { \
00115         register16_t regname; \
00116         struct \
00117         { \
00118             register8_t regname ## L; \
00119             register8_t regname ## H; \
00120         }; \
00121     }
00122 
00123 #ifdef _DWORDREGISTER
00124 #undef _DWORDREGISTER
00125 #endif
00126 #define _DWORDREGISTER(regname)  \
00127    __extension__  union \
00128     { \
00129         register32_t regname; \
00130         struct \
00131         { \
00132             register8_t regname ## 0; \
00133             register8_t regname ## 1; \
00134             register8_t regname ## 2; \
00135             register8_t regname ## 3; \
00136         }; \
00137     }

00517 /* Destination adress reload mode */

00963 /* NVM Command */
00964 typedef enum NVM_CMD_enum
00965 {
00966     NVM_CMD_NO_OPERATION_gc = (0x00<<0),  /* Noop/Ordinary LPM */
00967     NVM_CMD_READ_CALIB_ROW_gc = (0x02<<0),  /* Read calibration row */
00968     NVM_CMD_READ_USER_SIG_ROW_gc = (0x01<<0),  /* Read user signature row */
00969     NVM_CMD_READ_EEPROM_gc = (0x06<<0),  /* Read EEPROM */
00970     NVM_CMD_READ_FUSES_gc = (0x07<<0),  /* Read fuse byte */
00971     NVM_CMD_WRITE_LOCK_BITS_gc = (0x08<<0),  /* Write lock bits */
00972     NVM_CMD_ERASE_USER_SIG_ROW_gc = (0x18<<0),  /* Erase user signature row */
00973     NVM_CMD_WRITE_USER_SIG_ROW_gc = (0x1A<<0),  /* Write user signature row */
00974     NVM_CMD_ERASE_APP_gc = (0x20<<0),  /* Erase Application Section */
00975     NVM_CMD_ERASE_APP_PAGE_gc = (0x22<<0),  /* Erase Application Section page */
00976     NVM_CMD_LOAD_FLASH_BUFFER_gc = (0x23<<0),  /* Load Flash page buffer */
00977     NVM_CMD_WRITE_APP_PAGE_gc = (0x24<<0),  /* Write Application Section page */
00978     NVM_CMD_ERASE_WRITE_APP_PAGE_gc = (0x25<<0),  /* Erase-and-write Application Section page */
00979     NVM_CMD_ERASE_FLASH_BUFFER_gc = (0x26<<0),  /* Erase/flush Flash page buffer */
00980     NVM_CMD_ERASE_BOOT_PAGE_gc = (0x2A<<0),  /* Erase Boot Section page */
00981     NVM_CMD_WRITE_BOOT_PAGE_gc = (0x2C<<0),  /* Write Boot Section page */
00982     NVM_CMD_ERASE_WRITE_BOOT_PAGE_gc = (0x2D<<0),  /* Erase-and-write Boot Section page */
00983     NVM_CMD_ERASE_EEPROM_gc = (0x30<<0),  /* Erase EEPROM */
00984     NVM_CMD_ERASE_EEPROM_PAGE_gc = (0x32<<0),  /* Erase EEPROM page */
00985     NVM_CMD_LOAD_EEPROM_BUFFER_gc = (0x33<<0),  /* Load EEPROM page buffer */
00986     NVM_CMD_WRITE_EEPROM_PAGE_gc = (0x34<<0),  /* Write EEPROM page */
00987     NVM_CMD_ERASE_WRITE_EEPROM_PAGE_gc = (0x35<<0),  /* Erase-and-write EEPROM page */
00988     NVM_CMD_ERASE_EEPROM_BUFFER_gc = (0x36<<0),  /* Erase/flush EEPROM page buffer */
00989     NVM_CMD_APP_CRC_gc = (0x38<<0),  /* Generate Application section CRC */
00990     NVM_CMD_BOOT_CRC_gc = (0x39<<0),  /* Generate Boot Section CRC */

02549 
02550 /*
02551 ==========================================================================
02552 IO Module Instances. Mapped to memory.
02553 ==========================================================================
02554 */
02555 
02556 #define VPORT0    (*(VPORT_t *) 0x0010)  /* Virtual Port 0 */
02557 #define VPORT1    (*(VPORT_t *) 0x0014)  /* Virtual Port 1 */
02558 #define VPORT2    (*(VPORT_t *) 0x0018)  /* Virtual Port 2 */
02559 #define VPORT3    (*(VPORT_t *) 0x001C)  /* Virtual Port 3 */
02560 #define OCD    (*(OCD_t *) 0x002E)  /* On-Chip Debug System */
02561 #define CLK    (*(CLK_t *) 0x0040)  /* Clock System */
02562 #define SLEEP    (*(SLEEP_t *) 0x0048)  /* Sleep Controller */
02563 #define OSC    (*(OSC_t *) 0x0050)  /* Oscillator Control */
02564 #define DFLLRC32M    (*(DFLL_t *) 0x0060)  /* DFLL for 32MHz RC Oscillator */
02565 #define DFLLRC2M    (*(DFLL_t *) 0x0068)  /* DFLL for 2MHz RC Oscillator */
02566 #define PR    (*(PR_t *) 0x0070)  /* Power Reduction */
02567 #define RST    (*(RST_t *) 0x0078)  /* Reset Controller */
02568 #define WDT    (*(WDT_t *) 0x0080)  /* Watch-Dog Timer */
02569 #define MCU    (*(MCU_t *) 0x0090)  /* MCU Control */

07129 #define FUSE_WDWP1  (unsigned char)~_BV(5)  /* Watchdog Window Timeout Period Bit 1 */

07136 #define FUSE_BODPD1  (unsigned char)~_BV(1)  /* BOD Operation in Power-Down Mode Bit 1 */
07137 #define FUSE_BODACT0  (unsigned char)~_BV(2)  /* BOD Operation in Active Mode Bit 0 */
07138 #define FUSE_BODACT1  (unsigned char)~_BV(3)  /* BOD Operation in Active Mode Bit 1 */

07148 #define FUSE_SUT0  (unsigned char)~_BV(2)  /* Start-up Time Bit 0 */
07149 #define FUSE_SUT1  (unsigned char)~_BV(3)  /* Start-up Time Bit 1 */
07150 #define FUSE4_DEFAULT  (0xFF)

07154 #define FUSE_BODLVL1  (unsigned char)~_BV(1)  /* Brown Out Detection Voltage Level Bit 1 */
07155 #define FUSE_BODLVL2  (unsigned char)~_BV(2)  /* Brown Out Detection Voltage Level Bit 2 */
